==English==

===Noun===

'''gradient wind'''

# ([[Meteorology]]). Any [[horizontal wind velocity]] [[tangent]] to the [[contour line]] of a [[constant pressure surface]] (or to the [[isobar]] of a [[geopotential]] surface) at or above 2,500 feet (762 meters).

